{"tid":812490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最後一次想念著你","createTime":"2018-09-09T16:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T17:40:29.000Z","uid":180992,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c4e57f4c86f48c54453ef55ed08a3f0010b5b8","tid":812490,"uid":180992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:14:03.000Z","msg":"四年了 第一眼見到你既感覺，第一次同你單獨相處<br />\n第一次睇你打籃球，第一次心動...好多回憶我都仲記得<br />\n我地好小有合照因為知你唔鍾意影相，所以唯一一張既即影即有我到依加都仲擺係銀包到，每次fd見到都問我係咪未放低你，我每次都答放左，其實根本就未放。<br />\n<br />\n但我知我係時候要放手，放過自己同埋俾機會自己開心下，四年入面為左棵樹而放棄整個樹林。唸翻起都覺自己好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後一次再度記起"},{"pid":"41c164b960c19c23c918c0dc10bf9c0081b299f3","tid":812490,"uid":207522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 施主早日放下自在</span>"},{"pid":"b8af82406c401e8bb5439382907e9d2bf5223eef","tid":812490,"uid":95195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fef2a9cd5bb07da10c9b8d35d0395710426e56","tid":812490,"uid":180992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41c164b960c19c23c918c0dc10bf9c0081b299f3","tid":812490,"uid":207522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 施主早日放下自在</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:30:32.000Z","msg":"同自己講左四年放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef10010d1b51fb699f76af3dca0eef027278fa2b","tid":812490,"uid":180992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8af82406c401e8bb5439382907e9d2bf5223eef","tid":812490,"uid":95195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face